# helm — subchart .tgz files are committed alongside Chart.lock so a fresh
# `git clone` can `helm install` immediately, no `helm dependency build` step.
# Trade-off: ~5MB of binary blobs in the repo. Worth it for single-command
# deploys on fresh clusters.
# When bumping subchart versions: run `helm dep update deploy/helm/ai-radar`
# and commit both Chart.lock and the new .tgz files together.
